# Task 16 – Troubleshooting

## Project

Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Description

This task involved identifying, testing, and resolving configuration issues in the Smart Library Request Workflow application.

## Troubleshooting Areas

- Flow Execution & Logs
- Reference Qualifier
- UI Policy
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- Reports

## Issues Resolved

- Verified Borrow Request Approval Flow execution.
- Fixed Book Reference Qualifier.
- Validated Return Date UI Policy.
- Corrected Borrow Request ACL permissions.
- Ensured Most Borrowed Books report counted only approved requests.

## Testing

All components were retested after applying fixes and passed successfully.

## Technologies Used

- ServiceNow
- Flow Designer
- Access Control Lists (ACLs)
- UI Policies
- Reports
- Reference Qualifiers

## Status

Completed
